Global Women's Sports Footwear Market Insights
Women's Sports Footwear Market size was valued at USD 27.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 43.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.9% from 2024 to 2030.

Women's Sports Footwear Market Overview
The women's sports footwear market has experienced significant growth in recent years, driven by increasing participation in fitness and sports activities among women worldwide. As of 2024, the global market value for women's sports footwear is estimated to be over USD 70 billion, with a projected compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.5% from 2025 to 2030. Factors such as technological innovations in footwear, fashion trends, and the rise of athleisure have also contributed to market expansion. The market is dominated by well-established players, but new entrants and local brands are also gaining traction, offering products that cater to diverse consumer preferences.

